snippet.title: 10x10 - ZX Spectrum [Longplay]
snippet.description:
What do you think of 10x10?
This is a longplay of the ZX Spectrum version which was released in 2000.
The video will show a full walkthrough and display the gameplay.

Did you play this game or have any opinion on what you can see?
Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Completion Criteria: Solve the Puzzle

Developed by: Cyber, Qazix, Dexter, Nikolay Zhirov
